task.summary: Added option for file stores to delete files they cannot parse. Updated client loader too. https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/151 https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/150 https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/149
Refactoring client configurations to allow for using a QDL ini file. Trying to decouple XML from configurations. Implemented QDL ini file parsing for the command line client.
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/153 get the issuer from the well-known page for the command line client since checks are now failing for the ID tokens.
Merge from 5.4.3. Also updated CILogon QDL installer so it runs without invoking other build manually.
Fix https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/157 Updated tests and refactored testing harness to remove duplicate code blocks.

Added ability in QDL to simply set the file source claim and be done with it. This allows for having a file source in the virtual file system and therefore completely under QDL's control. Also refactored testing code.
Fix https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/159. Client management endpoint should preserve the grace period, not zero it out (thereby disabling grace periods for any unwitting clients.)
First part of fixing https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/161. refactored test code
Partial commit of large-scale refactoring of tests. Found an issue in the ID token Handler where downscoping on refreshes would not quite work right.
https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/166 check for missing/empty refresh token explicitly in refresh endpoint and fail immediately if it is not there.

https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/169 https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/170 https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/171
Nice refactoring of some classes too.
Added automated tests for WLCG. general cleanup before release.
Improvements in the FS migration tool. Updated the documentation, sql scripts. Added a test utility for QDL flow tests.
Tripped over ancient html that does not work in xhtml. Fixed.
merge from master. Updated tests, documentation and the fix for https://github.com/ncsa/oa4mp/issues/176
